column5:
I mean it is my favorite game of all time so I think you should give it a try.
If you do everything slowly and carefully you'll have to spend a bunch of hours in the game

Take it slow
Enjoy the little things
Do side missions
Meet strangers 
Spend time in the camp
Explore the world
Don't look for Gevin
It would be hard to fit it in the storyline. But maybe as young Arthur?
Skate and smoke is one of my favorite hobbies

To be honest i think that getting other pet is the best thing you can do
It would be the best tribute you can give to your cat
Good luck with your life

Happy cake day :)
Hope you get better
